  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260540/extras/d7739cf01bf3b4cf163c185ab675445e.avif?t=1678201805\" width=600 height=180 /></span><br><br><br><strong>Endless Nesla</strong> is a demanding infinite runner game with dynamic and precise movement mechanics.<br><br><br>Vi must escape from the Nesla. Cross the different sectors of the spaceship, collect data, and avoid obstacles of all kinds. Will you make it?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characteristics</h2><br>-Recover hidden data<br>-Unlock Endless mode by escaping the spaceship<br>-Confront your best score with the community<br>-Many achievements to unlock<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260540/extras/8b2d0f01f56672988d6aeb52f907ca88.avif?t=1678201805\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><br><br>You will fail.. several times, but it will only make you stronger !",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260540/extras/d7739cf01bf3b4cf163c185ab675445e.avif?t=1678201805\" width=600 height=180 /></span><br><br><br><strong>Endless Nesla</strong> is a demanding infinite runner game with dynamic and precise movement mechanics.<br><br><br>Vi must escape from the Nesla. Cross the different sectors of the spaceship, collect data, and avoid obstacles of all kinds. Will you make it?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characteristics</h2><br>-Recover hidden data<br>-Unlock Endless mode by escaping the spaceship<br>-Confront your best score with the community<br>-Many achievements to unlock<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260540/extras/8b2d0f01f56672988d6aeb52f907ca88.avif?t=1678201805\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><br><br>You will fail.. several times, but it will only make you stronger !",
